# Gmail AI Assistant

A lightweight Gmail AI assistant that:

- Connects to Gmail with OAuth2
- Fetches recent inbox emails
- Summarizes emails with OpenAI
- Classifies emails into:
  - Important
  - Promotional
  - Personal
  - Requires Reply
- Applies Gmail labels
- Drafts replies
- Lets you approve and send replies manually

